{"id":"d3b00296-0b0d-4622-96be-f86083a39310","name":"The Chase sisters","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>(CW: Vore)</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">(Char. by <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://aryion.com/g4/user/Lampton\" target=\"_blank\">Lampton</a>) </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"I hate this family...\" — <em>Any of the Chase sisters</em></p><hr><p>There is one rule in this voracious world that is impossible to avoid: \"it's eat or be eaten,\" one that can be throughly explored in the dysfunctional Chase family. From the intern garbage can that is <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c6df4f51-4cac-4e60-a5be-b38a26929b65_character-eliza-chase\" target=\"_blank\">Eliza</a>, to the wild girl of the night that is <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/00c0c5e9-3987-4853-a79a-9f05be64d992_character-elena-chase\" target=\"_blank\">Elena</a>, and the ever cautious <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6ddb1778-8aab-455a-8a4a-d26009d8bf17_character-ellie-chase\" target=\"_blank\">Ellie</a>, the Chases have many flavors (no pun intended) to their chaos, either being the predators or being the prey.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SJ5Iu77MikAT-3fI7Y6o3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Es6i-WKz08X8DMKk4Jx3s.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Ui58BD3YvQUyFqCkDacar.webp","creator":"NomNom88857","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":2041,"messages":28080,"created_at":"2025-09-20T18:53:04.928492+00:00"}